snippet.title: Out of hands - Gameplay Show Case
snippet.description: Out of Hands is a thrilling title that blends video-collage graphics with gripping psychological horror. Will you seek the truth that lurks shrouded in a wicked, warped world—and can you bear its weight? Misty memories threaten to tear you apart, and contort you into a being made... Out of Hands.
